{"about_the_game":"<strong>In this demo you can play two different levels of the game, with a bit of exploration, puzzling and combat.</strong><br><br>What happens when nobody dies anymore? The answer is far from pleasant: Chaos. Absolute, unending chaos that desperately needs to be cleaned up. But before the world can return to balance, the Grim Reaper itself must figure out what went wrong.<br><br>Welcome to <strong>Spindle</strong>, an old-school action-adventure where you step into the role of Death. But you're not alone on your journey through this strange, chaotic world \u2013 your trusty sidekick, an ever-loyal pig, will be with you every step of the way. More than just a cute little creature, your companion is vital to your mission to restore the natural order.<br><br>Are you ready to face the chaos head-on? Then <strong>grab your scythe, bring your pink buddy, and dive into a fantastic adventure!</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698620/extras/PNG1.png?t=1732284070\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Be the one and only Death<br></li><li>Enjoy a beautiful handcrafted pixel world<br></li><li>Explore grim dungeons<br></li><li>Solve puzzles<br></li><li>Pet the Pig</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698620/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732284070","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698620/page.bg.jpg?t=1732284070","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698620/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732284070","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698620/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732284070","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_descri